mmunication\u2011style issues, whereas the other candidates each lack essential teamwork or exhibit interpersonal weaknesses that could jeopardize safe, coordinated flight operations.\n**My vote:** Candidate\u202fC\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_3\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
